comments.content: This is currently not a pathway but a list of sleep related genes and proteins. The source for this information is the gene ontology. The genes and proteins were filtered for "sleep" annotation (taxon = homo sapiens). According to supplementary information they were clustered in major (neurotransmitters, hormons, appetite regulation and immune system) and minor groups.
